“这在颤抖的《Sketch Artist》中最为明显。值得注意的是，这是她的第一张个人专辑，尽管其作者确实留下了巨大的遗产，但这是一张令人惊讶的唱片。” </p><figure id="attachment_3571786" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3571786" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3571786" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="金·戈登《The Collective》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2007" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x803.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1397.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kim-Gordon-The-Collective-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1072.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3571786" class="wp-caption-text">金·戈登《The Collective》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>《The Collective》曲目列表如下：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.《再见》</strong><br /> <strong>2.《糖果屋》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“我不会迷失自己的想法”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“我是一个男人”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“奖杯”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“里面很黑暗”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“迷幻高潮”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“树屋”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“货架温暖”</strong><br /> <strong>10.《信徒》</strong><br /> <strong>11.“梦想美元”</strong></p><p>戈登还透露了一系列支持“The Collective”的美国巡演日期。这位歌手将于 3 月 21 日在佛蒙特州的 High Ground 演出。从那里，她将在华盛顿特区、纽约皇后区、洛杉矶和文图拉等城市停留，然后在旧金山的菲尔莫尔结束旅程。门票将于当地时间